images.title: A stunning Spanish sunset
images.caption: A stunning Spanish sunset
images.desc: Today’s image might look like the perfect setting for a classic American western, but you’ll have to travel a little further to visit this desert. The Bardenas Reales, located in the north of Spain, is home to plenty of lunar landscapes which surfaced millions of years ago - during a time that the inland sea which occupied the territory withdrew, leaving behind sediments that gradually eroded into amazing geological formations.
